-- Hermes to Propose Exceptional Dividend of 5 Euros a Share
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2012-03-22T05:12:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-22/hermes-to-propose-exceptional-dividend-of-5-euros-a-share.html
Hermes International (RMS)  SCA will
propose an exceptional dividend of 5 euros a share in addition
to a regular 2011 dividend of 2 euros.  Net income in 2011 climbed 41 percent to 594.3 million
euros, the company said in a statement in Les Echos newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  